    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/cdb547e3c795457c5bfe942137deb3a4.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;COROCONNECT&quot; 是一款考验团队合作的多人动作游戏。每位玩家将通过独特的机关操作，在精确的时机与队友默契配合，逐步挑战复杂的关卡。与好友或线上伙伴并肩作战，一起攻克所有关卡吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/07f638f88da90c8dcaef386fc652b6cf.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;COROCONNECT&quot; 当前处于抢先体验阶段，欢迎大家分享宝贵的意见与建议！不论是漏洞反馈、改进建议，还是创意点子，我们诚挚期待与你们共同打造更好的游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/a31644d1d576e2bc165a93bac0db45ed.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专为多人设计的游戏内容</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持本地与在线联机，最多可 4 名玩家参与</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家的操作至关重要，独特的玩法鼓励队友之间的充分合作与默契</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的机关系统：玩家可以自由切换四种不同机关，灵活运用能够让闯关更轻松。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/04d02cb7b981b04185ec912f67b05c68.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COROCONNECT支持远程同乐功能，但除了1P（主机玩家）以外的玩家无法使用键盘和鼠标进行游戏。若2P至4P参与游戏，请务必使用手柄进行操作。</strong></p>",
